  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1064">
<l>iṭamellāṅ koḷḷāt takaittē yiṭaṉillāk </l>
<l>kālu miravollāc cālpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even the whole world cannot sufficiently praise the dignity that would not beg even in the midst of destitution.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
